{"tid":1383511,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"校巴上的物資","createTime":"2019-07-29T16:57:40.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-29T16:59:28.000Z","uid":61242,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"741812fccd4a7c59cdb16ad72e02d55aa2409eeb","tid":1383511,"uid":61242,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T16:57:40.000Z","msg":"[member]<br />\n<br />\n經過琴日係海港政府大樓做校巴既家長綜合經驗：<br />\n<br />\n校巴擺定濕紙巾，食水，食物，生理鹽水，紗布/膠布，口罩<br />\n<br />\n男裝/女裝衣服 可以既有兩三個Size<br />\n<br />\n因為特別係前線既可能已經中左催淚彈，受左傷要即走！ <br />\n<br />\n最好包括自己外有多一個異性家長同行方便照顧。<br />\n<br />\n記住記住：家長我地一定要照顧好自己，如果我地中左催淚彈，受左傷。仔仔就放唔到學，我地安全佢地先安全。<br />\n<br />\n記住入tg group/ Zello 留意即時交通資訊。<br />\n<br />\n［/member]"},{"pid":"3cb14581675da4350ba10fd69dc378474229dab4","tid":1383511,"uid":110851,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T16:58:22.000Z","msg":"你個加密fail<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">光復香港 時代革命</span></span><br />\n唔睇都埋嚟推下po<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n[集思廣益]香城online小地圖app<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1383244\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1383244</a>"},{"pid":"ff85217d283cd7e29f1db396202a8fabc96c0659","tid":1383511,"uid":61242,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3cb14581675da4350ba10fd69dc378474229dab4","tid":1383511,"uid":110851,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T16:58:22.000Z","msg":"你個加密fail<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">光復香港 時代革命</span></span><br />\n唔睇都埋嚟推下po<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n[集思廣益]香城online小地圖app<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1383244\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1383244</a>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T16:59:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}